<bug>
    <id>3270</id>
    <title>Reader: Following tags appears to succeed while logged out.</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Nexus 4, OS 5.1.1</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">While logged out of wpcom, tap the tag on a post card to preview the tag.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">Notice there is a follow button present in the preview header.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.3">Tap the button and notice you are now "following" the tag.... while logged out.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.4">The tag will appear in the topic drop down, however, it will be purged after tapping the Gear icon.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">For consistency with sites should following tags be unavailable while signed out?</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
